<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .totalCare {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px 0px rgb(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .giustif {
            color: white;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: justify;
            text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 1px lightblue, 0 0 1em lightblue, 0 0 0.2em lightblue;
        }
        .blueBoat {
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px lightblue, 0 0 1em lightblue, 0 0 0.2em lightblue;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="totalCare">
        <div class="desk">
            <h4 class="blueBoat">BLUE BOAT COMPANY</h4>
            <p class="giustif">
                Vivi un'esperienza unica, attraversando la città di Amsterdam con il battello
                della Blue Boat Company. Avrai a disposizione degli auricolari per poter ascoltare
                la storia di questa fantastica città.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="https://www.insolitamsterdam.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ia_crociera-in-battello-amsterdam.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://cdn-imgix.headout.com/tour/5166/TOUR-IMAGE/e11173ef-55f0-414e-8089-55db0978fbc9-3324-amsterdam-sightseeing-cruise-02.jpg?w=744&h=465&auto=compress%2Cformat&crop=faces&fit=min" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://www.amsterdam.net/it/wp-content/uploads/sites/20/crociere-canali-amsterdam.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://www.viviamsterdam.it/images/viviamsterdam/Tour_in_battello/Crociera-Amsterdam-Cover.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://www.blueboat.nl/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/IMG_9611_low_res-scaled-960x600.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
